<DocsLayout title="Company Settings" section="Company Setup">
  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Company Settings is your command center for tailoring Field Promax to meet your unique business needs.
    By customizing these settings, you'll streamline operations and unlock the full power of the platform.
  </p>
  <p>
    Once configured, you'll be ready to explore key modules including Work Orders, Invoices and Payments,
    Mobile App, Schedule and Dispatch, Estimates, Customer Management, Dashboard and Reports, Timekeeping,
    Notifications, and more.
  </p>

  <h2>How to Access</h2>
  <img src="/images/company-setup/companysettings_01.jpg" alt="Company Settings Navigation" />
  <ul>
    <li>From the main menu, select <strong>Settings</strong> → <strong>Company</strong> to access company settings</li>
    <li>Select <strong>Settings</strong> → <strong>Manage Users</strong> to configure user settings</li>
    <li>Select <strong>Settings</strong> → <strong>Manage Lists</strong> to customize drop-down lists</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Key Settings</h2>

  <h3>Work Order Settings</h3>
  <p>
    Customize your work order templates with custom fields, scheduling options, and more.
    Configure your work orders to capture the information most important to your business.
  </p>

  <h3>Mobile App Settings</h3>
  <p>
    Set preferences for your mobile app, allowing technicians to create work orders, estimates,
    and manage tasks directly from their mobile devices.
  </p>

  <h3>Text Message Service Settings</h3>
  <p>
    Configure text message notifications for both technicians and customers. Ensure appointments,
    updates, and reminders are never missed.
  </p>

  <h3>Estimate Settings</h3>
  <p>
    Customize how estimates are generated, including terms and conditions, branding, and approval workflows.
  </p>

  <h3>Tax Settings</h3>
  <p>
    Manage multiple tax rates and assign them to different work orders or estimates based on
    location and service types for accurate compliance.
  </p>

  <h3>Service Request Settings</h3>
  <p>
    Set up service request forms and receive instant notifications when customers submit requests
    through your website.
  </p>

  <h3>PDF Settings</h3>
  <p>
    Personalize PDF templates for work orders and estimates. Add your branding, custom fields,
    and adjust the layout to match your needs.
  </p>

  <h3>Calendar Settings</h3>
  <p>
    Configure your company's calendar with business hours, time intervals, and appointment visibility
    to optimize your scheduling process.
  </p>

  <h3>Start-up Page Settings</h3>
  <p>
    Customize the landing page your team sees when they log in, giving them quick access to
    what matters most.
  </p>

  <h3>External User Settings (Customer Portal)</h3>
  <p>
    Set up external user accounts with limited access to your system, enabling secure communication
    and collaboration with clients.
  </p>

  <h3>Google Review Settings</h3>
  <p>
    Configure automatic Google Review requests after service completion to build your online reputation.
  </p>

  <h2>User Permissions</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Only <strong>Administrators</strong> have access to modify company settings</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Tips</h2>
  <div class="callout callout-tip">
    <p>
      Take time to customize these settings when you first set up Field Promax. Proper configuration
      ensures everything runs smoothly as you use the rest of the platform's features.
    </p>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
